
Shift-Left:
Early defect detection
Early in SDLC (requirements/design/coding)
Cheaper and faster to fix defects

Agile:
Iterative delivery & collaboration
Throughout each sprint
Continuous feedback, faster delivery

Relation:
Agile promotes continuous testing in sprints.
Shift-Left is an approach used in Agile to move testing earlier.
They complement each other: Agile is the process, Shift-Left is the testing philosophy.
